      "role": "user",
      "content": "i tried talking to people but they just tell me \"it gets better\" or \"just hang in there\" and it feels like they aren't even listening. it doesnt feel like it's gonna get better. it just feels like a never ending cycle of stress. i'm just so incredibly tired of fighting for a life that feels this heavy.",
